name: Sweet Lullaby
description:
I listened to the raindrops at the dawn, tapping on my window like a sweet lullaby, putting me to sleep. But the garden outside was starting to wake up, each leaf with drops of water trickling down. No one knew that she was slowly drinking it with great pleasure. 

Dimensions: ‪1,325 x 2,048‬
Fractal droplets dripping over Glazed window.
